{"notes":[{"id":1,"title":"• FILTER BASED ","body":"• Filter based on Active Cell<div><br></div><div><div style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; line-height: 19px; white-space: pre;\"><div><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Sub</span> <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">FilterByActiveCell</span>()</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Dim</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> DataRange </span><span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Range</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Dim</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> Target </span><span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Range</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #6a9955;\">' Set Target as the cell you currently have selected</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Set </span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Target</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> ActiveCell</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Set </span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">DataRange</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> Target.CurrentRegion</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #6a9955;\">' Check if the cell is within a data range and not empty</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #c586c0;\">If</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">Not</span> <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">Intersect</span>(<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Target</span>,<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> DataRange</span>) Is<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\"> Nothing</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">And</span> Target.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Value</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">&lt;&gt;</span> <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">\"\"</span> <span style=\"color: #c586c0;\">Then</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #6a9955;\">' Field is calculated by the relative position of the active cell in the range</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; DataRange.AutoFilter Field:<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span>Target.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Column</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">-</span> DataRange.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Column</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">+</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">1</span>,<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> _</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Criteria1:<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span>Target.Value</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #c586c0;\">Else</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">MsgBox</span> <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">\"Please select a cell within your data range.\"</span>,<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> vbExclamation</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #c586c0;\">End If</span></div><div><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">End Sub</span></div></div></div>","date":"5/11/2026, 11:24:38 AM"},{"id":2,"title":"• JUST LIKE CTR","body":"• Just like Ctrl + D but Only Formatting<div><br></div><div><div style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; line-height: 19px; white-space: pre;\"><div><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Sub</span> <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">FillDownFormatting</span>()</div><div><br></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Dim</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> selectedRange </span><span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Range</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Dim</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> topCell </span><span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Range</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #6a9955;\">' Work only with the currently highlighted cells</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Set </span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">selectedRange</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\"> Selection</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #6a9955;\">' Identify the top row of the selection to use as the \"Source\"</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Set </span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">topCell</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> selectedRange.<span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">Rows</span>(<span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">1</span>)</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #6a9955;\">' Copy the formatting from the top cell/row and paste to the whole range</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; topCell.Copy</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; selectedRange.PasteSpecial Paste:<span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">xlPasteFormats</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #6a9955;\">' Clear the clipboard \"marching ants\"</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Application</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">CutCopyMode</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\"> False</span></div><div><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">End Sub</span></div></div></div>","date":"5/11/2026, 11:26:38 AM"},{"id":3,"title":"• REPLICATE 🎉 DOUBLE ","body":"• Replicate 🎉 Double Click for Autofill in Excel<div><br><div><div style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; line-height: 19px; white-space: pre;\"><div><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Sub</span> <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">SatisfyingAutoFill</span>()</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Dim</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">lastRow</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Long</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Dim</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Range</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Dim</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">startRow</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Long</span>, <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">endRow</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Long</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Dim</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">i</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Integer</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Dim</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">chunkSize</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">As</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Long</span></div><div>&nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Set</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">ActiveCell</span></div><div>&nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">' Logic Change: Look DOWN from the current row in the left colum</span><span style=\"color: #f44747;\">n</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">' This stops at the first blank cell it encounters</span><span style=\"color: #f44747;\">.</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">lastRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">Cells</span>(<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Row</span>, <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Column</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">-</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">1</span>).<span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">End</span>(<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">xlDown</span>).<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Row</span></div><div>&nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">' Safety check: If the adjacent column is empty or row is huge, don'</span><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">t</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">run</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">If</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">lastRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">&gt;</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Rows</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Count</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Or</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">lastRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">&lt;=</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Row</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Then</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">MsgBox</span> <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">\"No contiguous data found in the left column.\"</span>, <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">vbExclamation</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Exit</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Sub</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">End</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">If</span></div><div>&nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">' Reset the visual animation logi</span><span style=\"color: #f44747;\">c</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">chunkSize</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> (<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">lastRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">-</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Row</span>) <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">/</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">10</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">If</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">chunkSize</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">&lt;</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">1</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Then</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">chunkSize</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">1</span></div><div>&nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">startRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Row</span></div><div>&nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">For</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">i</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">1</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">To</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">10</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">endRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">startRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">+</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">chunkSize</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">If</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">endRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">&gt;</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">lastRow</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Or</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">i</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">10</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Then</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">endRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">lastRow</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Range</span>(<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span>, <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">Cells</span>(<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">endRow</span>, <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">sourceCell</span>.<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Column</span>)).<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">FillDown</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">DoEvents</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Application</span>.<span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">Wait</span> (<span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Now</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">+</span> <span style=\"color: #dcdcaa;\">TimeValue</span>(<span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">\"0:00:01\"</span>) <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">/</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">10</span>) <span style=\"color: #ce9178;\">' Slightly faster paus</span><span style=\"color: #f44747;\">e</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">startRow</span> <span style=\"color: #d4d4d4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">endRow</span></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Next</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">i</span></div><div><span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">End</span> <span style=\"color: #9cdcfe;\">Sub</span></div></div></div></div>","date":"5/11/2026, 2:00:08 PM"},{"id":"12645c31-a6ef-4d92-b45a-adee6eac12a9","title":"TRIAL VERSION","body":"<div>Trial Version</div><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"XOWONA Two-Piece Triangle Bikini Set ...\">&nbsp;","date":"5/12/2026, 1:10:39 PM"},{"id":"306ba4a3-c797-43c5-865c-035a5cf52870","title":"1969 FORD MUSTANG MACH","body":"1969 Ford Mustang Mach 1 given 986bhp twin-turbocharged V8<div><img src=\"https://media.evo.co.uk/image/upload/s--X-WVjvBW--/f_auto,t_content-image-full-desktop@1/v1581606140/evo/2020/02/Ford%20Mustang%20Mach%201-5.jpg\" alt=\"1969 Ford Mustang Mach 1 given 986bhp twin-turbocharged V8 | evo\"></div><div>2015 Ford Mustang GT.</div><div><img src=\"https://images.collectingcars.com/058449/mainimage.jpg?w=1263&amp;fit=fillmax&amp;crop=edges&amp;auto=format,compress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;q=85\" alt=\"2015 Ford Mustang GT for sale by auction in Kristianstad, Sweden\"></div>","date":"5/12/2026, 2:24:31 PM"},{"id":"7792b78b-d485-4db5-9edd-7953064c0c61","title":"😎 SECRET FOLDER IN WI","body":"😎 Secret Folder in Windows<div><br></div><div><div>Vault Access: Harshit's CopyFlow</div><div>Use these commands in Command Prompt to toggle the visibility and system status of your folder.</div><div><br></div><div>🔒 Ghost Mode (Hide &amp; Protect)</div><div>This doesn't just hide the folder; it marks it as a critical system file so it won't show up even if \"Show Hidden Files\" is turned on.</div><div><br></div><div>attrib +h +s \"C:\\Users\\mlpit.SURYAMLPR\\Documents\\Harshit\\CopyFlow\"</div><div><br></div><div>+h → Sets the Hidden attribute.</div><div>+s → Sets the System attribute (super-stealth).</div><div><br></div><div>🔓 Reveal Mode (Unhide)</div><div>Bring your files back into the light with a quick reversal.</div><div><br></div><div>attrib -h -s \"C:\\Users\\mlpit.SURYAMLPR\\Documents\\Harshit\\CopyFlow\"</div><div><br></div><div>-h → Removes the Hidden attribute.</div><div>-s → Removes the System attribute.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes</div><div><br></div><div>&gt; The \"Super Hidden\" Trick: By using +s, the folder remains invisible even if someone checks \"Hidden items\" in File Explorer. They would have to uncheck \"Hide protected operating system files\" in settings to see it.</div><div>&gt; Pro-tip: Stay organized. If you forget the path, you can't unhide it easily! Maybe keep a tiny text file note of your \"vault\" locations. 🗝️</div></div>","date":"5/12/2026, 1:58:12 PM"}]}